<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ل ز ز:</span> <span class="c2">(لَزَّهُ)</span> شَدَّهُ وَأَلْصَقَهُ وَبَابُهُ رَدَّ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْمُلَزَّزُ)</span> الْمُجْتَمِعُ الْخَلْقِ الشَّدِيدُ الْأَسْرِ وَقَدْ لَزَّزَهُ اللَّهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٨٢⦘ وَلَازَزْتُهُ لَاصَقْتُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>